        "notes": [
            {
                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae Jetson AGX Xavier\u2122 series, Jetson Xavier\u2122 NX, Jetson TX1, Jetson TX2 series (including Jetson TX2 NX), and Jetson Nano\u2122 devices (including Jetson Nano 2GB) in the NVIDIA JetPack\u2122 software development kit (SDK). The update addresses security issues that may lead to denial of service, escalation of privileges, and impact to data integrity and confidentiality.<br><div><br></div><div>To protect your system, download and install the latest NVIDIA JetPack SDK from <a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/embedded/downloads\">Jetson Download Center</a>.</div>",
                "title": "Summary"
            },
